==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Air pump
<hw>Air" pump`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>. <sn>1.</sn> <fld>(Physics)</fld>
<def>A kind of pump for exhausting air from a vessel or closed space;
also, a pump to condense air or force it into a closed space.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Steam Engines)</fld> <def>A pump used to exhaust
from a condenser the condensed steam, the water used for condensing, and
any commingled air.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Air sac</ent>⟦br⟧
